{"tid":764323,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人女友條件太好 所以質疑自己係咪真心","createTime":"2018-08-02T01:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T01:02:15.000Z","uid":24607,"like":7,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"54e8392b7cc364ed82b54fc6f6057da96bb9de1b","tid":764323,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"同咗女友拍咗幾個月拖<br />\n雖然細我4年 入世未算深<br />\n但無論樣 身材 同性格 都好高分 <br />\n可算係少數10分會畀9分嗰種女仔<br />\n反觀自己唔算靚仔 又唔大隻 又冇錢<br />\n但佢成日買嘢送畀我 又幫我執房 煮好飯等我放工<br />\n過幾個月仲一齊租屋住<br />\n搞到我有時分唔清<br />\n究竟我係真心鍾意佢<br />\n定係純粹覺得執到寶所以咁投入段關係"},{"pid":"5610b31bcd3948e78d620e3812562329fb4fbdbc","tid":764323,"uid":41524,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:19:36.000Z","msg":"你發緊夢"},{"pid":"a119228296d0a5077271aab0daa8b6e1d9a099ca","tid":764323,"uid":117947,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:19:51.000Z","msg":"Ff少陣"},{"pid":"6bfc2b3ef47f454170e6cf42a0a0c42169b81c81","tid":764323,"uid":180124,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:20:02.000Z","msg":"質疑佢會唔會變心先啦"},{"pid":"1d8e87223192cb01b4810960aa65b7b249f1771c","tid":764323,"uid":24607,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:22:45.000Z","msg":"我自己都覺得好唔真實 但我真係冇ff<br />\n佢仲好到 我平時返工由朝忙到晚<br />\n真係一句wtsap都冇時間覆<br />\n但佢從來冇怨言 <br />\n一放lunch即刻覆佢佢就秒回我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好內疚"},{"pid":"b0a2619192a2bffb3cf7479b973a208d66547752","tid":764323,"uid":78873,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T01:24:07.000Z","msg":"講咁多做乜, 對人好啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ad48cdd0ae86918a3db1b7070d6f6fdb52290d","tid":764323,"uid":24607,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6bfc2b3ef47f454170e6cf42a0a0c42169b81c81","tid":764323,"uid":180124,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyT